Name: ZONEX
About the game: ZONEX is a 3D realtime dynamic effects showcase. Use traditional WASD controls to enter different rooms with various realtime dynamic 3D effects. Explore visual effects ranging from shapeshifting floors, moving plasma cubes, floating shapes to repeating waves. No unlocking needed. PC, SteamVR and Oculus support included.
